        <abstract>
            <p>Will propose GHL for the Linnean Society.</p>
            <p>Writes of his objections to GHL’s views.</p>
            <p>Considers Weismann’s remarks on the importance of the nature of the organism as well as conditions of life in determining variability have much truth.</p>
